summary: First mod on the Skyrim Nexus, Just a simple Player Shack in the Whiterun hold. Some good game is in the immediate area for your hunting pleasure!
descriptionHtml:
Whiterun Hunter\'s Shack

=====================
=====================
Simply a player shack in the midst of the Whiterun hold, near the western watchtower. It is way to escape the crowded city and take in the wonderful scenery. 

Includes:
All crafting areas (forge smelter enchaning table ect.)
Archery targets  
Weapon Racks
Mannequin
Small Garden
And the wonderful scenery!

Nothing special really, just a way for me to get firmilliar with the Skyrim Nexus. The shack is an interior (which was probably bad judgement on my part). Just dont look between the ceiling shingles. 

=====================
=====================

If you like the file endorse ect ect ect. An endorsement would make my day. 

Be nice people, first mod on skyrim nexus <Remember when criticizing
author: Jk KILER
